  "description": "<i>Fortuna</i> is a game based on the TV show Wheel of Fortune. The players take turns guessing letters to form a word or a saying. The game can be played with up to three players. During their turn the players can spin the wheel, guess a consonant, buy a vowel or guess the password. The game is divided into five stages. After each winning stage the player may buy a prize from the shop. Semi final stage allows to choose only a consonant, the winner takes all the prizes and goes to the last stage. In the final stage the player may select four consonants and one vowel.",
